**Root Cause:** The `sectionCollapseStates` Map in `DashboardPanelContainer` is never initialized from the section config values. Unlike `panelCollapseStates` which has an initialization effect (lines 225-240), `sectionCollapseStates` starts empty and only gets entries when the user toggles a section.

