2. Config is updated with `collapsed: true` via parent callback
3. On remount or section changes, `sectionCollapseStates` resets to empty Map
4. Render falls back to `section.group?.collapsed` which is `true`
5. Section stays hidden; toggle attempts don't work as expected because state is out of sync

